{"article_id":"nLzcrjcNxIMMfjzt","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Democratic lawmakers on Saturday rejected President Donald Trump 's proposal","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to extend some non-permanent protections for Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals recipients and individuals with Temporary Protected Status","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"in exchange for border wall funding .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Trump floated the offer in an afternoon speech from the White House ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"however ,","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Democrats see the lack of a permanent solution for the individuals","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"impacted by these programs","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"as a deal-breaker .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"The plan","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Trump proposed","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"also includes $ 800 million for urgent humanitarian assistance and $ 805 million for drug detection technology","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to secure ports of entry ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"as well as additional border agents , law enforcement officials and new immigration judge teams","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"to deal with cases of migrants","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"crossing the US-Mexico border .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"But all of this is on the condition","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that he receives $ 5.7 billion for a border wall","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"-- the central point of contention between Democrats and Republicans in the fight","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"to re-open the government .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"Prior to Trump 's speech , Pelosi , a California Democrat , issued a statement in response to `` initial reports ''","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"that `` make clear","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that his proposal is a compilation of several previously rejected initiatives ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"each of which is unacceptable","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"and in total , do not represent a good faith effort","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"to restore certainty to people 's lives . ''","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"Her statement continued :","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"`` It is unlikely that any one of these provisions alone would pass the House ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"and","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"taken together ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"they are a non-starter .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"For one thing , this proposal does not include the permanent solution for the Dreamers and TPS recipients","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"that our country needs","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"and supports . ''","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"Following Trump 's speech ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Pelosi tweeted ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"`` What is original in the President 's proposal is not good .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"What is good in the proposal is not original .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Democrats will vote next week to add additional border security funding for ports of entry , advanced technology","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"for scanning vehicles for drugs","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"& immigration judges . ''","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Republicans issued statements of support for the President 's proposal ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"including McConnell ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"who said","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"he intends to bring the legislation forward this week .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"He had declined earlier to bring forward spending bills","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Democrats passed in the House .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"`` I commend the President for his leadership","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"in proposing this bold solution","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"to reopen the government ,","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"secure the border ,","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"and take bipartisan steps","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"toward addressing current immigration issues , ''","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"McConnell said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"The Republican from Kentucky called the proposal a `` a fair compromise","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"by incorporating priorities from both sides of the aisle . ''","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"`` This bill takes a bipartisan approach","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"to re-opening the closed portions of the federal government .","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"It pairs the border security investment","depth":15},{"id":59,"text":"that our nation needs","depth":15},{"id":60,"text":"with additional immigration measures","depth":15},{"id":61,"text":"that","depth":16},{"id":62,"text":"both Democrat and Republican members of Congress believe are necessary .","depth":16},{"id":63,"text":"Unlike the bills","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"that have come from the House over the past few weeks ,","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"this proposal could actually resolve this impasse .","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"It has the full support of the President","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"and could be signed into law","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"to quickly reopen the government , ''","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"he continued .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Schumer , a New York Democrat , called the proposal `` more hostage taking . ''","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"`` It 's clear the President realizes","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"that","depth":16},{"id":73,"text":"by closing the government","depth":18},{"id":74,"text":"and hurting so many American workers and their families ,","depth":18},{"id":75,"text":"he has put himself and the country in an untenable position , ''","depth":17},{"id":76,"text":"Schumer said in a statement .","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"`` Unfortunately , he keeps putting forward one-sided and ineffective remedies .","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"There 's only way out :","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"open up the government , Mr. President ,","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"and then Democrats and Republicans can have a civil discussion","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"and come up with bipartisan solutions . ''","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"His statement continued :","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"`` It was the President","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"who singled-handedly took away DACA and TPS protections in the first place","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"-- offering some protections back in exchange for the wall is not a compromise","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"but more hostage taking . ''","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"Rubio , a Florida Republican , also issued a statement in favor of Trump 's latest offer .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"`` The way","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"to end this shutdown","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"is for both sides to make mutual concessions","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"in order to reach an agreement .","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"The President has made a very reasonable offer","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"to extend DACA and TPS protections in exchange for the border security measures","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"he supports .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"I hope","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"instead of choosing the road of endless obstruction ,","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"Democrats will decide to work with him","depth":16},{"id":99,"text":"to reach an agreement","depth":17},{"id":100,"text":"and end the shutdown , ''","depth":17},{"id":101,"text":"Rubio said in a statement .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"The Illinois Democrat is the co-author of the BRIDGE Act ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"which is legislation","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"aimed at extending protection for DACA recipients ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"and issued a statement","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"also rejecting the President 's proposal .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"`` First , President Trump and Senate Majority Leader McConnell must open the government today .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Second , I can not support the proposed offer","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"as reported","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"and do not believe","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"it can pass the Senate .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"Third , I am ready to sit down at any time","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"after the government is opened","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"and work","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"to resolve all outstanding issues , ''","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"Durbin said .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"The Virginia Democrats ,","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"who represent many thousands of government employees in their state next to Washington , DC ,","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"issued a joint statement","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"criticizing the President","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"for not acknowledging `` the pain and suffering ''","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"he has caused to those affected by the shutdown","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"the first step to immigration reform needs to include reopening the government .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"`` President Trump 's remarks today failed to acknowledge the pain and suffering","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"he has caused to federal workers , contractors , and millions of Americans with this unnecessary government shutdown ,","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"and his rhetoric toward immigrants was inflammatory and unproductive , ''","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"the statement said .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"It continued ,","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"`` We would be glad to review ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"starting this week ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"any proposals","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"he has","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"to responsibly improve and increase border security","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"and provide certainty to TPS recipients and DREAMers .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"To start this process ,","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"we have to immediately reopen the government . ''","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"West Virginia Democratic Sen. Joe Manchin weighed in on the President 's announcement in a tweet on Saturday evening ,","depth":3},{"id":139,"text":"saying","depth":4},{"id":140,"text":"he was `` hopeful ''","depth":5},{"id":141,"text":"that this proposal would allow the government to open soon .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":283,"left":0,"right":282,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":282,"left":278,"right":281,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":278,"left":160,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":149,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":144,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":143,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":143,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":4,"right":147,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":5,"right":146,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":145,"right":8,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":155,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":152,"right":154,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":150,"right":151,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":13,"right":153,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":16,"right":157,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":17,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"purpose","nuc